Package: dann
Title: Discriminant Adaptive Nearest Neighbor Classification
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Trevor Hastie [aut], Gaurav Sood <gsood07@gmail.com> [cre]
Maintainer: Gaurav Sood <gsood07@gmail.com>
Description: Implements Discriminant Adaptive Nearest Neighbor classification,
    a method that adapts the distance metric based on local discriminant
    analysis to improve nearest neighbor classification.
